REM android_settings_search.duck
REM Opens the Android Settings search — useful for demonstrating
REM that the paired "keyboard" has system-level access.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE ON
HUMAN_SPEED SLOW

HOME
DELAY 1200

STRING settings
DELAY 800
ENTER
DELAY 1800

REM Settings search bar - type to filter
STRING bluetooth
